name: OutTel GT Graphics cards
description: The OutTel GeForce RTX 3070 Noctua OC Edition 8GB GDDR6 Graphics Card is the first graphics card to feature Noctua fans and a heatsink that has been co-engineered by Noctua. This potent pairing allows the Outtel GeForce RTX 3070 Noctua Edition to operate at lower GPU temperatures and produce less noise than any air-cooled graphics card in its class. Outtel and Noctua have come together to deliver the quietest air-cooled graphics card in their class.

name: Outtel® Xeon Scalable Processors
description:
OutTel Xeon® Scalable processors benefit from decades of innovation for the most common workload requirements, supported by close partnerships and deep integrations with the world’s software leaders and solution providers.

A balanced architecture, optimized for many workload types and performance levels, all with the consistent, open, OutTel architecture you know and trust, that delivers built-in AI acceleration and advanced security capabilities, OutTel ® Xeon® Scalable processors allow you to place your workloads securely where they perform best-from edge to cloud.
